      "type": "markdown",
      "content": [
        "### **Lun**",
        "",
        "`Open` will need a **Logical Unit Number** (`LUN`) which is a integer identifier to reference a file.",
        "",
        "The lun **must be freed** once you are finished with it. A file associated with a active LUN will be locked or inaccessible for future operations until IDL exits.",
        ""
      ],
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
